comment: Ignore the sign that says for staff only; if someone asks, just say you'd prefer to use a gender neutral bathroom and they will be fine with it. If for some reason they aren't, the principal, Mr Smith, and the vice principal, Mr Copp, are very supportive of trans and gender nonconforming people; talk with either of them and situations will be settled in your favor.
